title: How Many Otters Could You Take On?
description: No, Seriously. How many could you take on? A new Christmas Favorite Musical Moments arrived on the show today as well as a new Christmas Wish (Grab the tissues), Drake had packages stolen from him, Can we turn normal songs into Christmas songs?, Talking with Johnathan Fogle, & More!
